Ollama Project Attribution

This Helm chart uses the Ollama project. The chart uses a custom-built Ollama image
(`ghcr.io/arktec-quant/ollama:v0.18.2-cuda-12.8`) that is built from scratch, not derived from the
official `ollama/ollama` Docker image.

Ollama is an AI Inference Engine for running large language models (LLMs) locally, developed and maintained by the Ollama project team.

Ollama Project:
- GitHub: https://github.com/ollama/ollama
